{"id":783071,"date":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":3}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"旧体诗词","genre":"","count":"64","ytitle":"","mtitle":"品菊归来","ftitle":"","authors":["秦瘦鸥"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦瘦鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晴日秋阳艳，名花集我乡:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千姿夺造化，百态胜姚黄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚节留三径，孤芳做雪霜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙潭水汩汩，似祝世义皇。"}]}